metadata.description: AWAKΞN is a poem written by David All as the brand ethos for ChangeDAO. It is dedicated to all of the Changemakers that tirelessly do their part to make the world a better place. /n/n/The NFT is a screenshot of the poem from David's personal phone. The interface embodies a spirit of a modern typewriter, and anchors the message in the digital age.
